Comptox Ontology Reference Guide¶

Release

Date

Sep 10, 2019

This reference manual describes the functions, modules, and objects included in (and associated with) Comptox Ontology - a centralized knowledge representation and knowledge base for computational toxicology.

Acknowledgements¶

Comptox Ontology’s documentation structure was adapted from the Numpy documentation (see Numpydoc <https://numpydoc.readthedocs.io/en/latest>).
